<li><a href='http://feeds.reuters.com/~r/Reuters/worldNews/~3/HzRJOI6-jwE/story01.htm'>Spain fishermen protest artificial reef in Gibraltar</a><br />
GIBRALTAR (Reuters) - Spanish fishermen protested against the creation of an artificial reef in the bay of Gibraltar on Sunday and claimed the territory's authorities were blocking their access to the waters in the latest focus of tensions between Spain and Britain.
<li><a href='http://feeds.reuters.com/~r/Reuters/worldNews/~3/ngldV6_eMe0/story01.htm'>North Korea accepts South's proposal to resume war-torn family reunions</a><br />
